posting_body: ['This charming 708 square foot apartment at Silver Ridge is waiting for you to make it your home.', 'You’ll be living on the third floor with one bedroom, vinyl wood floors, stainless steel appliances, and a spacious balcony.', 'This is right across from some beautiful trees and walking distance to the pool!', 'We are conveniently located 1.5 miles from the Sun Ray Shopping Center, and about 2 miles from Battle Creek Regional Park.', 'Close to downtown St. Paul and a quick drive to Woodbury, you’re sure to find exactly what you’re looking for!', '________________________________________', 'APARTMENT DETAILS:', '• Floorplan: Oak', '• Apartment #:30-108', '•', 'Rent starting at $1180.00/ mo.', '• 708 square feet', '• 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom', '• First floor', '• Vinyl wood floors (Updated within the past year)', '• Cabinetry (Updated within the past year)', '• Stainless steel appliances (Updated within the past year)', '• Balcony with a beautiful view of the trees', '•', 'In-building laundry', 'COMMUNITY AMENITIES:', '• Outdoor Pool', '• Fitness Center', '• Party Room', '• LuxerOne Package Locker', '• Charcoal Grills', '• Playground', 'CONTACT:', '• Visit <URL> or call', 'show contact info', '• Schedule a tour today!', '*PLEASE BRING IN A COPY OF THIS AD WHEN YOU VISIT TO RECEIVE AN ADDITIONAL $150 OFF YOUR FIRST MONTH’S RENT*', '*Price and availability determined by move-in date and subject to change', 'Managed by Bigos Management.']
